para1.text: AgriGO and gProfiler were used to assign GO terms to 130 genes involved in the physiological adaptation to the spaceflight environment in ARG1 KO cells (corresponding to the FArg: GArgFC signature). The results, including GO term names, ontology, transcript IDs, gene symbols, gene descriptions, and FArg: GArgFC (log2) values, are presented in Table 2 of the source document. Gene duplicates within oncology were removed and assigned to the most specific available GO term class.
